public abstract class UnpauseTransitionXCommand
extends TransitionXCommand<Void>

Transition command for unpause the job. The derived class has to override these following functions:

updateJob() : update job status and attributes unpauseChildren() : submit or queue commands to unpause children notifyParent() : update the status to upstream if any
